The feature typical of a trip of Czechs was in this epoch to take with one its own food preserved food, sausage, etc to economise.
Another important instant was also the interchangeability of the Czech crown which allowed to our tourists finally after dozens years it could freely buy the Western currency.
Our living standard as well as the average wage augmented what caused around year 1997 another important instant.
Thanks to an increasing request for trips travel agencies have begun since 1997 to prepare turns with links by air charter planes which thanks to contracts awfully reduced costs in comparison with what there was before.
