Year 2000 it became transferred to the capital of Valle and having does adequate courses, it specialised in dactyloscopie, which is the study of the skin of friction, that is to say palms and feet.
During the week of operation against alias Alfonso Cano they had informed in Eliazar to take clothes with him at least for three days.
Something very big waited for him.
On Friday at night he left for Cauca in a helicopter of Palmira.
